[[香港|香港]]於1959年首次參與[[奧斯卡最佳國際影片獎|奧斯卡最佳國際影片獎]]，其後39次角逐該獎項。奧斯卡最佳外語片獎由[[美國電影藝術與科學學院|美國電影藝術與科學學院]]頒發，為[[奧斯卡獎|奧斯卡]]中頒發給年度美國以外最佳非英語電影的獎項<ref name="Rules">{{cite web | title = Rule Thirteen: Special Rules for the Foreign Language Film Award | work = Academy of Motion Picture Arts、Sciences | publisher = [[Academy_of_Motion_Picture_Arts、Sciences|Academy of Motion Picture Arts、Sciences]] | url = http://www.oscars.org/awards/academyawards/rules/86/rule13.html | accessdate = 2013-08-26 | archive-date = 2013-07-30 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130730051948/http://www.oscars.org/awards/academyawards/rules/86/rule13.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。該獎項於2019年4月更名為「最佳國際影片獎」<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.forbes.com/sites/jeffewing/2019/04/24/academy-announces-rule-changes-for-92nd-oscars/#7b9d85ac3d5b |title=Academy Announces Rule Changes For 92nd Oscars |work=Forbes |accessdate=2019-07-12 |archive-date=2019-05-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190527181952/https://www.forbes.com/sites/jeffewing/2019/04/24/academy-announces-rule-changes-for-92nd-oscars/#7b9d85ac3d5b |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=ACADEMY ANNOUNCES RULES FOR 92ND OSCARS |url=https://www.oscars.org/news/academy-announces-rules-92nd-oscars |accessdate=2021-08-29 |work=Oscars.org {{!}} Academy of Motion Picture Arts and Sciences |date=2019-04-23 |language=en |archive-date=2019-04-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190424161332/https://www.oscars.org/news/academy-announces-rules-92nd-oscars |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last1=options |first1=Show more sharing |last2=URLCopied! |first2=Copy Link |title=Film academy is setting new inclusion standards for Oscars eligibility |url=https://www.latimes.com/entertainment-arts/movies/story/2020-06-12/film-academy-announces-new-inclusion-initiatives-systemic-racism |accessdate=2021-08-29 |work=Los Angeles Times |date=2020-06-12 |archive-date=2021-07-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210712145159/https://www.latimes.com/entertainment-arts/movies/story/2020-06-12/film-academy-announces-new-inclusion-initiatives-systemic-racism |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last1=Lawler |first1=Kelly |title=Academy to implement diversity standards for Oscars eligibility, set best picture at 10 nominees |url=https://www.usatoday.com/story/entertainment/movies/2020/06/12/oscars-academy-implementing-diversity-standards-eligibility/3174801001/ |accessdate=2021-08-29 |work=USA TODAY |archive-date=2021-08-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210829090110/https://www.usatoday.com/story/entertainment/movies/2020/06/12/oscars-academy-implementing-diversity-standards-eligibility/3174801001/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.forbes.com/sites/jeffewing/2019/04/24/academy-announces-rule-changes-for-92nd-oscars/#7b9d85ac3d5b |title=Academy Announces Rule Changes For 92nd Oscars |work=Forbes |accessdate=2019-07-12 |archive-date=2020-05-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200512231634/https://www.forbes.com/sites/jeffewing/2019/04/24/academy-announces-rule-changes-for-92nd-oscars/#7b9d85ac3d5b |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

香港、台湾以及中國大陆獲美國電影藝術與科學學會視為三個參賽單位，各自遞交電影參賽。在香港方面，每年由香港電影製片家協會挑選影片角逐奧斯卡<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.fso-createhk.gov.hk/tc/guidetofilming_index.php?page=3&sub_topic_id=7 |title=電影業團體及相關組織 |access-date=2021-03-03 |archive-date=2018-10-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181009151326/https://www.fso-createhk.gov.hk/tc/guidetofilming_index.php?page=3&sub_topic_id=7 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

迄今[[杜琪峯|杜琪-{峯}-]]和[[許鞍華|許鞍華]]各有四部参选为最多之香港导演，[[李翰祥|李翰祥]]有三齣電影獲選代表香港，而[[岳楓|岳楓]]、[[韋家輝|韋家輝]]、[[胡金銓|胡金銓]]、[[羅啟銳|羅啟銳]]、[[嚴浩|嚴浩]]和[[王家衞|王家衞]]則各有兩齣電影獲選。

歷年的提交名單當中，只有10部電影同為[[香港電影金像獎|香港電影金像獎]]的「[[香港電影金像獎最佳電影|最佳電影]]」，包括《似水流年》、 《女人四十》 、 《香港製造》、 《千言萬語》、 《無間道》 、 《大隻佬》 、 《桃姐》 、 《一代宗師》、《黃金時代》 及 《少年的你》 。

香港遞交的電影於2002年和2004年因不符合資格而被取消資格。

